%% TechEx AI system design diagram
flowchart LR
  subgraph Client[Browser / React App]
    UI["Styled UI\n+ 3D Orb"]
    Hooks["Voice + SSE Hooks"]
    MapModal["Map & Guide Modals"]
  end

  subgraph Server[Bun API Server]
    TextSvc["TextChatService\nSSE /api/chat"]
    VoiceSvc["VoiceChatService\nWS /api/ws"]
    KeyMgr["ApiKeyManager\nAPI key rotation"]
    KB[("data/db.json\nKnowledge Base")]
  end

  subgraph Gemini[Google Gemini APIs]
    TextModel[gemini-2.5-flash]
    LiveModel["gemini-2.5-flash-\nnative-audio"]
  end

  UI -->|Chat UI actions| Hooks
  Hooks -->|Text requests<br/>JSON + history| TextSvc
  Hooks -->|PCM audio over WS| VoiceSvc
  VoiceSvc -->|Audio responses + map triggers| Hooks
  TextSvc -->|Show map events| MapModal

  TextSvc --> KB
  VoiceSvc --> KB
  KeyMgr --> TextSvc
  KeyMgr --> VoiceSvc

  TextSvc -->|Rotating Gemini keys| TextModel
  VoiceSvc -->|Rotating Gemini keys| LiveModel
  Hooks <-->|SSE deltas| TextSvc
  Hooks <-->|Voice state events| VoiceSvc

  KB -. preload .-> Server
